Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
saveColorPreference(25.10)                          saveColorPreference(25.10)

Name
       saveColorPreference - Saves color preferences for the Innovus main dis-
       play as specified in the Color Preferences form

Syntax
       saveColorPreference

       [-help]

       [-dir <string>]

       [-include_customized]

        -name <string>

       Saves  color  preferences  for the Innovus main display as specified in
       the Color Preferences form.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each saveColorPreference parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man saveColorPreference

       -dir <string>
              Specifies the directory path. By default, the  color  preference
              file is saved in the current directory.

       -include_customized
              Includes the settings in the Customize Tab form within the Color
              Preferences form.

       -name <string>
              Specifies the name of the color preference file.

